cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with modal logic and its applications to agency and game theory. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper introduces a new modal logic and discusses its properties. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with logics of agency and games. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) are relevant categories as the paper discusses game theory and its applications. Finally, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly deal with machine learning, but it may be relevant in the context of the transfer of complexity results.
